{"type": "article", "id": 23040, "title": "agape 极简浴缸", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103912LwDop6PGdB5Ye3nu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是西班牙女设计师 Patricia Urquiola 为意大利品牌 agape 推出的一系列浴缸，造型传统而极简。cuna 是由不锈钢管框架支撑了水盆，很轻盈。而 larian 则显得方正典雅许多，边缘略有向内倾斜，是一种开放的姿态，水缸之外的细长的水龙头成为具有对比性的装饰，有些是黑白相对的。而他们从前合作的 vieques 是由钢铁制作的，另带有柚木书架与靠背放在浴缸的边缘，很有趣。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071039115FU9HPrEKcWBe6Gg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.69682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103911dDTQYy01JABl65j4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103911qHQrPVFSLRl0CeMs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103912KTZxOGL9XWBEb3Qv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66136919\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}